@startuml
title Pair Class with File Operations

class Pair {
  - first: int
  - second: double
  + Pair()
  + Pair(int, double)
  + getFirst() : int
  + getSecond() : double
  + setFirst(int) : void
  + setSecond(double) : void
  + operator-(const Pair&) : Pair
  + operator+(int) : Pair
  + operator+(double) : Pair
  + operator<(const Pair&) : bool
  + operator==(const Pair&) : bool
}

class main {
  + {static} main() : int
}

Pair : + friend operator<<(ostream&, const Pair&) : ostream&
Pair : + friend operator>>(istream&, Pair&) : istream&

main ..> Pair : uses
main ..> saveToFile : calls
main ..> loadFromFile : calls
main ..> displayAll : calls
main ..> createAndSave : calls
main ..> readAndDisplay : calls
main ..> deleteLessThan : calls
main ..> increaseByL : calls
main ..> addAfterPosition : calls

note top of Pair
  Overloaded operators:
  - subtraction
  - addition with int/double
  - comparison (< and ==)
  - stream operators
end note

@enduml
